'''盐芽孢杆菌属'''（学名：''Halobacillus''），也称'''喜盐芽孢杆菌属'''，是[[芽孢桿菌科|芽孢桿菌科]]的一种革兰氏阳性菌<ref>LPSN lpsn.dsmz.de[https://lpsn.dsmz.de/genus/halobacillus] {{Wayback|url=https://lpsn.dsmz.de/genus/halobacillus |date=20201025143822 }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/45667 |title=UniProt |access-date=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2020-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513020000/https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/45667 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。胞内产生芽孢，细胞呈杆状或球状到卵圆形。发现于盐的生境中。该属的模式种为嗜盐盐芽孢杆菌（''Halobacillus halophilus''）<ref> Halobacillus gen. nov., with Descriptions of Halobacillus litoralis
sp. nov. and Halobacillus trueperi sp. nov., and Transfer of
Sporosarcina halophila to Halobacillus halophilus comb. nov.[https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Stefan-Spring/publication/237574784_Halobacillus_gen_nov_with_Descriptions_of_Halobacillus_litoralis_sp_nov_and_Halobacillus_trueperi_sp_nov_and_Transfer_of_Sporosarcina_halophila_to_Halobacillus_halophilus_comb_nov/links/00b7d51bf5873673d5000000/Halobacillus-gen-nov-with-Descriptions-of-Halobacillus-litoralis-sp-nov-and-Halobacillus-trueperi-sp-nov-and-Transfer-of-Sporosarcina-halophila-to-Halobacillus-halophilus-comb-nov.pdf]</ref>。

